data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house located in the desirable city of Wilmington, NC. This home offers a comfortable and inviting living space for anyone looking to settle down in a vibrant community. The house features a spacious patio and a fenced yard, perfect for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the beautiful weather. As a resident, you will have access to not one, but two community pools, providing ample opportunities for relaxation and recreation. Additionally, tennis enthusiasts will appreciate the convenience of the on-site tennis courts, allowing for friendly matches and staying active. The community clubhouse is another fantastic amenity, offering a space for socializing and hosting events. Whether you're looking to unwind by the pool, engage in a friendly tennis match, or simply enjoy the tranquility of your own private yard, this house has it all. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this delightful house your home. Contact us today to schedule a tour and experience the wonderful lifestyle this community has to offer.

NO Smoking 
Pets Allowed with Approved Pet Screening

Holly Shelter
